-- France Telecom Targets 300 Million Clients Worldwide by 2015, Tribune Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-05T04:48:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/france-telecom-targets-300-million-clients-worldwide-by-2015-tribune-says.html

          
          
             France Telecom SA is seeking to
increase its worldwide client total to 300 million by 2015, from
190 million currently, La Tribune reported, without saying where
it got the information.  
 Chief Executive Officer Stephane Richard will present his
strategic plan today, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        